<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ASCII"?>
<caldef:CalDefinitionFile xmlns:caldef="http://www.caltools.gm.com/caldef" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <CalDefFileVersion>7</CalDefFileVersion>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>1</Version>
    <Date>11APR14</Date>
    <Description>Deleted ENABLE_APPLICATIONTRAY_DMC3. Deleted ENABLE_APPLICATIONTRAY_INTERIOR_LIGHTING. Deleted VALET_COMBO_DIGITS_SUPPORTED. Deleted VALET_COMBO_FLASH_FREQUENCY. Deleted VALET_COMBO_FLASH_TIME.</Description>
    <Author>Matthew Highstrom</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>4</Version>
    <Date>9/3/2015</Date>
    <Description>Removed the VALET_MASK_MENU CAL that was in this CalDef file, as there is already a duplicate CAL for this already being used in the GIS507_Settings.caldef file. </Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>2</Version>
    <Date>29SEP14</Date>
    <Description>Added Usage on LOW, MID, and HIGH</Description>
    <Author>Scott Rush</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>3</Version>
    <Date>4/17/2015</Date>
    <Description>Per request from Sanghyun Ryu updated ENABLE_APPLICATION_DMC3, ENABLE_APPLICATION_INTERIOR_LIGHTING, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_ALL_TERRAIN, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_COMFORT, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_ECO, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_NORMAL, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_OFF_ROAD, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_SNOW, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_SNOW_ICE, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_SPORT, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_TOUR, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_TOW_HAUL, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_TRACK, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_TOW_HAUL, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_TRACK, ENABLE_DMC3_MODE_WEATHER,  MWS_PANE_PASSENGER_VIEW_DELAY, MWS_PANE_AUTO_DISMISS_TIMER, MWS_PANE_MINI_MODE_TIMER, and MWS_PANE_SUPPRESSION_TIMER cal to remove usage of Low Radio.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>5</Version>
    <Date>2/28/2017</Date>
    <Description>Within the HMIExternalVehicleFeatures.caldef file, removed the following two calibrations: 1.) ENABLE_APPLICATION_DMC3 and 2.) ENABLE_APPLICATION_INTERIOR_LIGHTING calibrations since the GM User Interface Team (Cody Hansen and Derek Fraser) confirmed these two specific calibrations were legacy calibrations used for NGI that are not intended to be used for Info3.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>6</Version>
    <Date>6/15/2017</Date>
    <Description>Updated the usage field for all of the calibration to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>7</Version>
    <Date>27MAR2019</Date>
    <Description>Added 'ENTRY_VCU' and 'VCU' tags for initial creation of VCS compatible CalDefDatabase for version GIS-646 V6.0.0 release.</Description>
    <Author>Scott Rush</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
